Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.24,0:22:41.49,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}如果我不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.49,0:22:46.45,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}你还能够说是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.45,0:22:51.75,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}崩坏的砂器散落一地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.84,0:22:57.06,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}破碎的心能否重新拾起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.08,0:23:06.22,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}何人的呼唤 幻化为耳鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.22,0:23:11.17,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}时间似乎静止
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.28,0:23:14.22,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}啊 觉醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.22,0:23:19.12,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}冲破这无边的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.40,0:23:24.27,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}疾风一般逃离
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.63,0:23:29.25,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}曾如行尸走肉一般
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.25,0:23:36.22,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}我们 到城墙之外 再相见吧
